  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2456120/extras/0c4f9940109c546304f56d6c9f0d08ac.avif?t=1772725924\" width=608 height=79 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2456120/extras/eedd7041da07b4f5be8d68ec40bf66c2.poster.avif?t=1772725924\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2456120/extras/eedd7041da07b4f5be8d68ec40bf66c2.webm?t=1772725924\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2456120/extras/eedd7041da07b4f5be8d68ec40bf66c2.mp4?t=1772725924\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Fully simulated physics!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Choose between the FUN or REALISTIC difficulty. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Endless fun! Refill the machine after winning a set amount of prizes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Collect and inspect 200 prizes! All fully 3D!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Various accessiblity options</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Special Prizes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special Prizes randomly appear. You have 3 attempts to win them, before they disappear again. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customize</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your arcade by importing your own image! All aspect ratios are supported. Simply drag and drop a .png or .jpg file into the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2456120/extras/699b0087cebd34a1933b743311814f47.poster.avif?t=1772725924\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2456120/extras/699b0087cebd34a1933b743311814f47.webm?t=1772725924\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2456120/extras/699b0087cebd34a1933b743311814f47.mp4?t=1772725924\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2456120/extras/0c4f9940109c546304f56d6c9f0d08ac.avif?t=1772725924\" width=608 height=79 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2456120/extras/eedd7041da07b4f5be8d68ec40bf66c2.poster.avif?t=1772725924\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2456120/extras/eedd7041da07b4f5be8d68ec40bf66c2.webm?t=1772725924\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2456120/extras/eedd7041da07b4f5be8d68ec40bf66c2.mp4?t=1772725924\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Fully simulated physics!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Choose between the FUN or REALISTIC difficulty. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Endless fun! Refill the machine after winning a set amount of prizes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Collect and inspect 200 prizes! All fully 3D!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Various accessiblity options</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Special Prizes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special Prizes randomly appear. You have 3 attempts to win them, before they disappear again. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customize</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your arcade by importing your own image! All aspect ratios are supported. Simply drag and drop a .png or .jpg file into the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2456120/extras/699b0087cebd34a1933b743311814f47.poster.avif?t=1772725924\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2456120/extras/699b0087cebd34a1933b743311814f47.webm?t=1772725924\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2456120/extras/699b0087cebd34a1933b743311814f47.mp4?t=1772725924\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
